Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting EIC Decision occurrences out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting EIC Decision across all cases
Percentage of variants that include SW-Awaiting EIC Decision followed by SW-EIC Accept
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Percentage of variants that include SW-Awaiting EIC Decision followed by SW-EIC Reject
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' out of all 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Percentage of variants that include SW-Awaiting EIC Decision followed by SW-EIC Major Revision
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' out of all 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: Percentage of variants that include SW-Awaiting EIC Decision followed by SW-EIC Minor Revision
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' out of all 'SW-EIC Minor Revision'

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting EIC Decision occurrences that are immediately preceded by SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' out of all 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting EIC Decision occurrences that are immediately preceded by SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed appears at least once
Metric: Number of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' occurs

Name: Percentage of cases containing SW-Reviewer Agreed that eventually reach SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' out of all 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Ratio of SW-Awaiting EIC Decision occurrences to SW-Reviewer Agreed occurrences
Metric: the average of the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Percentage of SW-Awaiting EIC Decision activities that occur after at least three reviewer-related activities (e.g., SW-Reviewer Agreed, SW-Reviewer Declined, SW-Reviewer No Response)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Frequency of SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in variants with performance duration above the median variant duration
Percentage of SW-Awaiting EIC Decision occurrences that lead to a final decision (SW-EIC Accept, SW-EIC Reject, SW-EIC Major Revision, or SW-EIC Minor Revision) within 7 days
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Percentage of all EIC-decision-related waiting states (including RW-Awaiting EIC Decision and RSW-Awaiting EIC Decision) that correspond specifically to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' out of all 'RW-Awaiting EIC Decision'
